{"type":"click","text":"1\n    \n      Animated Nav Tabs\n      A sliding pill/underline that glides between tabs with spring physics (like iOS segment control). The active indicator smoothly animates to the selected tab instead of jumping.\n      \n        \n          GRV Log\n          Inventory\n          Orders\n        \n        The white pill slides smoothly between tabs","choice":"nav-transitions","id":null,"timestamp":1774256541819}
{"type":"click","text":"1\n    \n      Animated Nav Tabs\n      A sliding pill/underline that glides between tabs with spring physics (like iOS segment control). The active indicator smoothly animates to the selected tab instead of jumping.\n      \n        \n          GRV Log\n          Inventory\n          Orders\n        \n        The white pill slides smoothly between tabs","choice":"nav-transitions","id":null,"timestamp":1774256542485}
{"type":"click","text":"2\n    \n      Page Content Transitions\n      When switching pages, content fades out/in with a subtle vertical shift. AnimatePresence handles exit animations so the old page gracefully leaves before the new one enters.\n      \n        \n          \n          \n        \n        →","choice":"page-transitions","id":null,"timestamp":1774256543060}
{"type":"click","text":"3\n    \n      Staggered Table Row Entrance\n      When data loads or filters change, rows appear one-by-one with a fast stagger (30-50ms delay between rows). Each row fades in and slides up slightly. Creates a \"waterfall\" effect that makes data feel alive.\n      \n        \n          \n          \n          \n          \n          \n        \n        Rows cascade in from top to bottom","choice":"table-rows","id":null,"timestamp":1774256544169}
